Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:08.37,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的夜晚  也不能停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:13.33,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始前行  等待着那份炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:18.50,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦肩而过的心完美地没有交汇点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:23.47,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那距黎明还遥遥无期的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:28.51,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们比隆冬的寒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:33.23,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加痴迷 虚幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:38.36,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中沉淀的那份雪白的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:43.36,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐涌溢  摇动我的坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.78,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是天空撒下的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:54.04,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是雪花凝结而成的羽翼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:57.38,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:02.47,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着那仅存的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:10.47,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧拥抱着你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:08.37,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,itetuku yoru tatitomarezu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:13.33,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bokura hajimaru netu wo matteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:18.50,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kurei ni suretigau kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:23.47,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yoake mo tousugiru mati de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:28.51,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bokura ha mahuyu no hosi yori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:33.23,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mutyuu de hakanai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:38.36,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mune ni otita siroi omoi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:43.36,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahuredasite boku wo yurasite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.78,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sora ga kobosita yasasisadakara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:54.04,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yuki ha yoseatta tubasa no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:57.38,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kini no kata wo tutumu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:02.47,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tada nukumori mamotte
